text: Otto Feyder (December 13, 1877 - February 10, 1961) was an American gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1877 births Category:1961 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Chicago
